Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:06.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:22.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:24.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:28.35,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:29.82,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:36.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:44.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:53.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:01:00.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:07.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:13.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:22.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:26.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:40.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:50.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let me help you, Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:52.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help! I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:54.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:54.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay!{\i0}\NAll right, then here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:06.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:18.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I call him Mitaro,\nthe All-Purpose Slicer & Dicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:21.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now your workload will be so much\nlighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:23.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do your thing, Mitaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:30.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:36.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. That was a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:40.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:47.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld's been latching herself onto\NBelldandy for the past few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:52.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She was separated from her beloved sister.\NYou can't blame her for wanting a{\i1}tt{\i0}ention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:55.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, listen to you! I'll bet deep down\ninside you're jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:56.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:03:00.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should let her mother you\nonce in a while, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.44,0:03:05.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:08.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going out somewhere, are\nyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:11.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm going to class with Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:12.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See you later!{\i0}\NAll right, we'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:24.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You stay at home like\na good little girl, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:31.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:37.30,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Teaching a Lesson Called\NCompetition?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well! Good morning, Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:48.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister, are you going to that place\nyou call ''college'' again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:54.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There are so many people there\nat college...it's a lovely place to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:57.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should come sometime, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:59.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go there for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:09.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Big Sister always goes off\nwith Keiichi because of this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:15.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What a primitive 2-wheel drive rig!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:19.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's making my beautiful\NBig Sister ride this piece of junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:21.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First, this side car... Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this inefficient fuel pump?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:28.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Just look at that clutch!\nIt's absolutely pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:31.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh, now that I can see...\nthere's no oil cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it isn't Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:42.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That bike you fixed for me the\nother day...it's running like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You really saved the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't mention it,\nyou're more than welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's my way of saying thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:55.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm sure! You're\nalways such a big help, Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, if you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:05:00.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The boss at the fish shop wants you\nto take a look at his bike, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:01.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure!{\i0}\nI'd really appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:08.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:13.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Megumi. What's up?\nIt's so early in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:16.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought I'd join\nyou guys for breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:21.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! Here. I brought you a gift.\NThe grocer gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:25.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You really do get around, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So unlike our Keiichi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:29.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, back off, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, gimme some more!{\i0}\NOh, it's you, Megumi! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:31.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Megumi! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}\NOh, it's you, Megumi! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:33.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy. Can I join you for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:35.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop it, Urd!{\i0}\NBelldandy. Can I join you for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:36.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:44.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I made all these\nmodifications in such a short time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I must be a genius after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did you do to my bike?{\i0}\N...I must be a genius after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:54.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't thank me,\nit was a piece of cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:57.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot I was going to take it apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:06:00.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...who knew I'd lose myself\nin the joy of creation instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:03.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!\nIs this your daughter, Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:07.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?\NThat's Belldandy's little sister, Skuld.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:08.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:11.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:11.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you attached a turbo, huh?{\i0}\nI may not look it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A turbo in front of the carburetor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, I'm talking to you!{\i0}\NA turbo in front of the carburetor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:22.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you had a hard time keeping the\ncarb balanced on both sides, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:26.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a no-brainer with\nsomething simple like a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:29.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but you could always go\nwith a fuel injector, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But then there'd be the problem of heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You did great, making a turbo this small.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's good!{\i0}\NYou did great, making a turbo this small.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:40.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately,\nnow the body's off-balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you criticizing my work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:48.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,According to my calculations, it should\nbe 1.5 times faster than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:51.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it's probably gotten\na speed boost, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:54.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it's too much for the chassis to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi! Get on and prove me right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, stop that!{\i0}\NKeiichi! Get on and prove me right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:02.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.\NThat'll give you a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:11.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:12.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}\NWho are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's Keiichi's younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:19.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're his sister...\nyou're not getting away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is for whoever dares\nto mock my inventions...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:24.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the Skuld Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's quite enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:33.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those who use such violent words end\nup with violence in their hearts also.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister, give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:36.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Belldandy to the rescue!{\i0}\NBig Sister, give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:39.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to compete,\nit must be on equal footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:40.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You three must be sisters after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, Big Sister!{\i0}\NYou three must be sisters after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:46.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monsters?{\i0}\NWell, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:58.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Den-chan missed you since you've been\nsuch a stranger these days, Morisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:01.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You keep your mouth shut about that!\N{\i1}Come on, you're too old to be so shy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um...so what is it that you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A Robot Battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:12.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These two will each build a robot,\nand compete against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A Robot Battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:19.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:22.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,X-1 Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's what he means.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:33.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could look into my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:36.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's it gonna be?\NWill you accept this challenge or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:38.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:42.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, building a robot sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:47.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you on, show you my power, and\nrub it in your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be looking forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:54.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're treating me like a kid again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:09:00.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to build the most awesome\nrobot and cut you down to size!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:07.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave the rest to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:09.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then... farewell, all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:16.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anything can happen with those two,\nhuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, it's a barrel-collecting race.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:27.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The robot that gathers the most steel\ndrums inside that ring wins the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Steel drums?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's so like those two to come up\nwith something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:35.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can use whatever materials\nyou want, and any number of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:40.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like you'll be allowed to use\nequipment and facilities at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Interference during the\ngame is also welcome.''
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those are my kind of rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:48.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm going to start\ndesigning my robot right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:53.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think it will be a\ngood experience for Skuld.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be so sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:02.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do understand the reason why\nyou fired up Skuld like that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that girl's more\ndifficult than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:10.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I think I'll go explain\nthe rules to our little Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}VICTORY!\NSKULD!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:23.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We are Skuld's groupies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:27.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to put our lives on\nthe line to support Skuld! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:31.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Megumi Morisato\NFan Club Community!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:35.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And together we're going to\nguide Megumi to victory! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What... what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:40.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My, you two are both so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:47.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is all pretty crazy,\nbut let's both do our best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:50.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I ever gonna lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:03.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:07.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Telling us we can use any materials\nwe want, and this is what they provide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, these are your materials!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}\NBehold, these are your materials!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:15.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are just too\nuncivilized to be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:18.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, there's Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the Megumi camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you're with the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:22.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since when did you go for that type?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:25.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what they're thinking...\N{\i1}Since when did you go for that type?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:27.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:31.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Skuld! Good luck, okay?\NWe're all rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:35.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are those the parts for your robot?\NWant us to help you carry them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:39.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um... you see... I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, they gave me such a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:51.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, you can just bring that here...\nthis way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:53.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Use that pipe for reinforcement, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:58.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay.{\i0}\NUse that pipe for reinforcement, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So she can't even build\na robot by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:04.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\nit should be a cakewalk for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, that's just what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Take that! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:28.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bam! Pow! Whack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:29.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:32.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:35.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I came to help out\nmy darling little sister, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be just fine on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:40.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything\nwe can do to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:46.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot of work for just one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:57.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right. I can build\na robot on my own just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:59.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like that Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:24.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's late coming back, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:30.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's wallowing\nin the joy of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:32.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go help after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:34.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just leave her alone.{\i0}\nI'm going to go help after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you encouraged her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:40.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to her now,\nshe'll only be more stubborn about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so you're actually worried too, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:47.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance! That kid doesn't even\nlook up to me as her older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:52.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty, I'm going to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:55.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:59.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I was mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:00.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:03.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld can be a little obstinate\nat times, but I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:08.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...deep down inside, she saw something\nin Megumi very much like herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:12.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why she's had\nsuch a chip on her shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:17.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there's also an aspect of herself that\ndiffers from Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:20.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanted her\nto find it on her own...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:22.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you tried to make them compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:28.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because I was sure that those\ntwo could become friends, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:35.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she's your sister\nand Urd's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:39.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, we can't just leave her\nto fend for herself like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...so I think it'll be okay\nto help her out in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:43.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:57.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a lot of headway tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:15:00.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think, Big Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:04.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to call it a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:10.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? Don't tell me it's a spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:18.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:21.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me happy to hear you say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:24.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But is it really okay to\ntreat us all like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:28.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All of us in the Nekomi Shopping Arcade\nare rooting for you, Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:31.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone, dig in\nand do your best for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Skuld.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is she doing reconnaissance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't care if she sees what we've got!{\i0}\nIs she doing reconnaissance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:44.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't you come eat with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:45.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:48.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she really can't stand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:51.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hear she's building\nher robot all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:58.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By herself, huh? That's pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:03.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the thing is, there are limits to\nwhat you can accomplish on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:13.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:37.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ROBOT BATTLE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:53.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}GO! SKULD!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:35.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}MEGUMI!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:45.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Robot Battle between Skuld\nand Megumi Morisato will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:52.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First... in the red corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:57.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With Skuld wielding the controls...\na machine called Hysteric Wheel #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:01.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the other corner...\NWith Megumi Morisato at the controls...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:05.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...a machine by the name\nof Pot Shaker Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:11.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've built a perfect robot! I wonder\nif you can defeat my creation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:14.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed that you've built\na robot like that by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I know that victory will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:21.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ready... fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:34.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See that?\NMy Hysteric Wheel #1 was designed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:38.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...pulverize anything within its\nspinning radius and then grab it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:42.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She made that? I know she's my sister,\nbut that's terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And you two are so alike it's terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:51.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so relaxed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:59.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:04.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's true your robot has overwhelming\npower, but it's not maneuverable enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:12.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi Morisato is on a tear,\ncollecting those cans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can she hang on for the win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:19.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm just going to cruise to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Skuld?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:27.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take a closer look at the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:28.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Interference during the\ngame is also welcome.''
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those are my kind of rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What an appalling rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:38.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, both of you!{\i0}\NWhat an appalling rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, both of you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:44.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your robot doesn't have\nany offensive functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:47.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me reduce you to scrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:56.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:19.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Seniors! What happens in a case like\nthis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:26.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since she gobbled up Skuld's robot,\nI'd have to say that means Megumi wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:36.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing for you to latch onto\ninside that drum... you can't destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:40.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no way, no way!\NThis just isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:43.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! You asked for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:01.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A self-destruct device,\nfor crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:03.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, pretty wild, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:06.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a lot of work,\ncleaning up this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:09.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Seniors! What happens in this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:10.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tamiya and Ohtaki ran off! Get them!{\i0}\NSeniors! What happens in this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tamiya and Ohtaki ran off! Get them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was a tie! Give us our money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:17.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:23.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:24.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:30.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to win next time, all right?\nI want you to let me help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:32.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:43.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I want you to make up with Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:46.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You built an awesome robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:53.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, let's build one together.\nI bet it'll be a lot more fun that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:56.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:57.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:58.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:03.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:07.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My robot was way more awesome than\nyours!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:08.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:13.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To think that's my own sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.32,0:22:15.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's just like you.{\i0}\NTo think that's my own sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:19.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?\NJust how is she like me? Tell me how!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:21.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know, in that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.53,0:22:25.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better say we're not\nalike right now! Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:25.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and your\NDreams. You have a wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:30.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and your\NDreams. You have a wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:35.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you so much it hurts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:41.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it hurts me that\nI can't tell you how I feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:46.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You and I have matching hearts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:51.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we must share the\nsame scars deep down inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:56.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now that I'm in your arms,\nI think I can catch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:23:01.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...your pounding heartbeat this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:07.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody else matters...\NAll we have to do is gaze at each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:12.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right for your heart to flutter...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:17.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:23.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't run away from happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:28.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always be waiting for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:33.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So come rest your wings anytime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:38.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right to cry...\nanytime you need to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:44.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want to see you again...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:49.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.59,0:23:55.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want you to be happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:59.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That which has been created...\nit is called a ''Machine.''
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:03.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A machine without a heart gains a\nsoul thanks to the goddess' love.
